#: ../../A/alpha-geek.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from animal ethologists' alpha male] The most technically accomplished or "
"skillful person in some implied context. \"Ask Larry, he's the alpha geek "
"here.\""
msgstr ""
"[動物行動学者のalpha male(ボスざる)から]ある暗黙の文脈において、技術的に最も達者または熟練した人物。「Larryに訊けよ、ここのalpha"
" geekだから」。"
